						<p><hi rend="bold">Vibhava (1688 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers the gift of a <hi rend="italic">kirīṭa</hi> to god Śrīraṅganāyaka by queen Muddamma in the year <hi rend="bold">Vibhava, Chaitra, bahuḷa.</hi> The week-day is not quoted and hence the date is not verifiable. The year corresponds to 1688 A.D.</p>						

